Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:04.40,italics,,0,0,0,,Just as expected
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:07.76,italics,,0,0,0,,of the Anti-Ajin Special Forces.\NIt’s not just a name.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:09.15,italics,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:11.15,italics,,0,0,0,,time for the last stage.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.35,italics,,0,0,0,,It’s your fault\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:14.99,italics,,0,0,0,,that my quiet life is all messed up!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.89,italics,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun, I-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:22.19,italics,,0,0,0,,hate people who get in the way of my \Ngames more than anything else!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.48,italics,,0,0,0,,Even though he’s unconscious...\NHow is the ghost still moving?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:28.20,italics,,0,0,0,,If you want a quiet life,\N I’ll grant that wish-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.96,italics,,0,0,0,,Ghost!\N Come out!!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:32.04,italics,,0,0,0,,Nagai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:33.98,italics,,0,0,0,,it’s okay!   \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.98,italics,,0,0,0,,Come out!!!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.84,italics,,0,0,0,,-forever, in the darkness.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.23,italics,,0,0,0,,You guys take the stairs!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.60,italics,,0,0,0,,Bring them under control!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:45.47,italics,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:50.38,italics,,0,0,0,,The EMP got rid of the electronic lock,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:53.23,italics,,0,0,0,,but we still haven’t gotten the analog key.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:56.84,italics,,0,0,0,,S- Satou-san?\NWe still didn't get his confession!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:01.93,italics,,0,0,0,,What will really prove our power\N is coming next.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:04.17,italics,,0,0,0,,We’ve captured Nagai Kei and Nakano Kou.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:06.76,italics,,0,0,0,,This will save a little face \Nfor the Committee.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:09.79,italics,,0,0,0,,Let’s go.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.11,upper,,0,0,0,,Continuing \Nour report from the scene.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:02.43,upper,,0,0,0,,According to those involved in the panic\N caused by the ajin Satou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.43,upper,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.94,upper,,0,0,0,,President Hashiguchi of \NMusashi Heavy Industries has been killed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:10.00,upper,,0,0,0,,and there have been heavy casualties among the \NAnti-Ajin Special Forces and riot police.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:10.00,upper,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:11.32,upper,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:14.40,upper,,0,0,0,,still no trace has been found as to how Satou escaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:18.08,upper,,0,0,0,, and police are increasing efforts all around to try and determine his whereabouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:23.48,upper,,0,0,0,,but due to the effects of the simultaneous attacks, a state of chaos has forces...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:28.81,upper,,0,0,0,,You guys look like you’ve been to a funeral.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:38.96,upper,,0,0,0,,What happened on the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.60,upper,,0,0,0,,Why did you let Satou go?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.38,upper,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tosaki-san!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.38,upper,,0,0,0,,How could you let things end \Nup in this sorry state?  \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With your IBM, you should have been\N able to take down Satou!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down, Tosaki-san!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To put all the blame on Nagai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s unfair.     \N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just as Suzumura-san says.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not only Nagai’s fault!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No... \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s my fault.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That Satou-san couldn’t be stopped...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That Hirasawa-san and the others were killed...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all my fault.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?         \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nagai!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We were live at the scene.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are also investigating
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the whereabouts of Tosaki Yuu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and Shimomura Izumi, members of the \NAjin Management Committee.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspects are-\NTosaki-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they are.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Tosaki-san?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re as big an idiot as ever.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s nothing left to be done.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s over.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the biggest idiot is me.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To join forces with ajin...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the result.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My salary all went down the drain.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I’m a real criminal!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling that others are\N dying because of you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Ghost!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out!!!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure there's been no mistake?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They’ve all been taken by Satou.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ahold of the Prime Minister immediately.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime Minister. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If word of this gets out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,all of Japan will be thrown into a panic!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re that dangerous?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If they use everything they’ve taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,they could kill the entire population of \NJapan three times over.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime Minister.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we should assume the worst,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and prepare a compromise?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue the search for Satou,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin preparations here.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the countdown has been completed.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the government gave us no response.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s truly unfortunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,, but as I’ve said previously,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,, our advance cannot be stopped.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,, within the next ten days, the third wave-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we will begin the final battle.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve come this far, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but to those of you who still think \Nyou’re not involved...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,well, there’s nowhere to run.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.23,upper,,0,0,0,,[TV announcer] What you are currently seeing is a is a new video taking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:58.19,upper,,0,0,0,,responsibility for today’s attacks that Satou\N has uploaded to ajin.net.  \N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How far are you planning to take this?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re really messing things up.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike lives, those can’t be replaced.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-san is just playing around!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s not thinking at all about \Nthe future of ajin!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,, Stop spacing out.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you thinking about what to eat?      \N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wasn’t.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,, Tanaka-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know....\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Satou really thinking about our-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,About ajin-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is trust Satou.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,however it goes, this is the last battle.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t that right,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-san?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.  \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be... the last.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With this.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you’re right. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the blueprints you asked for.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to get data on \Nthe drainage systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can finish that today.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your work, I'm sorry you had to be responsible for everything.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How are things over there?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be done in time.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of you, Okuyama-kun.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this will make things fun again.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last operation, right?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the other side’s reaction.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,, no particular reason.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But don’t worry.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I intend to genuinely\N negotiate with the government.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why we picked up ‘that’ from\N Musashi Heavy Industries.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But that’s right.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t keep playing at war forever.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s how it is.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,, I’ll get back to work.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Results of the investigation.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspicions have arisen that Professor Ogura \Nwas kidnapped by the ajin Satou.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll confirm the security of the safe house \Nwas suddenly attacked by Satou,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,, and report back again.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In summary, this is more or less what happened.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And following this last email,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Douglas Almeida and Carly Meyers disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,, and currently their whereabouts are unknown.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When we questioned the security at the safe house,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,they said they were attacked by a unit of a few people, including ajin. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have reports that after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,, a car chase took place in the\N vicinity of the safe house.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,, we can only conclude that Satou erased them. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as we thought, Satou has Professor Ogura captive.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we ask the Japanese government to intervene?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,, I don’t think they can handle Satou. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,sending another team might result\N in the same failure.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We can afford to wait for Satou’s \Nnext terrorist attack.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As we'd hoped,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,, this might require a military intervention.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If that’s how it turns out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we can even legally secure the ajin in Japan. \N(they want to steal the ajins)\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll send the report to the Secretary of Defense.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s that?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather’s nice today, too.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We broke through the front without even resorting to tricks!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the best show.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.36,upper,,0,0,0,,We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:33.47,upper,,0,0,0,,We have an emergency!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.15,upper,,0,0,0,,Terrorists armed with guns have invaded!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.62,upper,,0,0,0,,They set fire to the ammunition dump!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.99,upper,,0,0,0,,Unit on duty, head to point 4!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:42.19,upper,,0,0,0,,Confirmed that the terrorists are using automatic\N weapons and rocket launchers.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.46,upper,,0,0,0,,Other units, arm yourselves and move out!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.64,upper,,0,0,0,,Take positions quickly!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.94,upper,,0,0,0,,This is not a drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.83,upper,,0,0,0,,I repeat, this is not a drill!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.62,upper,,0,0,0,,We can’t use the vehicles?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.00,upper,,0,0,0,,The bullets are with the munitions!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these guys?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They came prepared!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take them down!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,can’t stop us!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,, kill them!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop them!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The ammunitions dump and armory have fallen.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have reports that the enemy are ajin!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The backup unit still isn’t ready?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re on their way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will take time before they arrive!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry them up!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What you are seeing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is the draft of the compromise with Satou,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,, prepared by the Ajin Management Committee.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime Minister. It’s an emergency.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A Ground Self-Defense Force base is under attack by Satou.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:21.20,upper,,0,0,0,,[background- I’d like to hear your opinions.]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:25.32,upper,,0,0,0,,[background- I hope to have things finalized\N by tonight. What do you think?]\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Tanaka.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve taken control here.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go ahead and transport our objective..\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll be done soon here, too.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Satou-san!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no way we can end this quickly!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t let them come any closer!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the others?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold out here until backup arrives!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim carefully!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re terrorists, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep killing them!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,W- What was that?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That ended pretty quickly, didn’t it?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then let’s finish taking control!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that took even less time than I expected.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Self-Defense Force is bound by law,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's a limit to what weapons they can use.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a good plan to take out the \Nammunitions dump and armory first.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-san’s video...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be prepared to support the backup unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,, Whatever we do, we have to hold out here!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t move!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know things were hard for you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was kind of Easy Mode, wasn't it?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime Minister.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the head of the base has passed away.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t be serious.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re pinpointing the important\N facilities, and taking control.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage continues to mount as the \Nfighting continues at the scene.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to reorganize the units,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,, they’re under retreat for the time being.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re just letting them do as they wish?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We won’t allow that.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Backup forces are already spreading out \Naround the outside of the base.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t fight back immediately?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also chemical weapons.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow us to handle them with caution.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all set.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okuyama-kun, \Nyou really are good with machines.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s no big deal.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a standard device.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem pretty impressive, but \Ncan we use them effectively? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re a new model with a lot \Nof military capabilities.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just imitate Okuyama again?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniper squad, in position.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrorists have taken hostages.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait to invade until we understand\N the inside situation.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-san.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finished setting up the missiles.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s restart the show!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s get right to the point.  \N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, including this one, twenty missiles\N filled with chemical gases are loaded
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and ready to fire.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Their effectiveness should be well-known.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,These lethal weapons were developed at \NMusashi Heavy Industries,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with Tanaka-kun as the guinea pig.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I’ll convey our demands.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,By twelve noon one week from now, I want you to hand over Japan.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There, we will create an independent\N country ruled by ajin. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over Japan?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What a crazy demand.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,, I understand that it’s a lot to ask.  \N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems that the government has no \Nintention of recognizing ajin rights,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forced to show our full strength.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With this lethal gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we will kill all the humans in this country!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We have plenty of reason to\N hold a council of war. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t allow him to fall into the hands \Nof the Japanese government.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All citizens should already know this, but...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,am very serious.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Screen- End of transmission]\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzumura.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I rely on you to procure weapons?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Procure weapons. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-  That is possible.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it obvious?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re stopping Satou.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We don’t have anything left-\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t matter.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,, Satou has killed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,, a large number of people.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And he will without hesitation\N kill many more. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,, This is no longer just my problem.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Suzumura. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I follow my orders. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s all there is for me to do.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirasawa-san would have said the same thing.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:21:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but we’re stopping Satou.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s get revenge for the old guys!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t do it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:08.00,board3,,0,0,0,,Next time, episodes 24 and 25 will air consecutively!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.80,preview,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:26.50,to be conti,,0,0,0,,To be continued...
